    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Well-kept older vehicle in good overall condition. It presents nicely for its age, with a clean interior and exterior, though you should still expect some normal cosmetic wear and minor signs of use consistent with an older car. It appears to have been cared for and should make a solid choice for someone looking for a respectable, usable vehicle without paying mint-condition money.",
