    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation for the right buyer. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking an inexpensive car with practical value and plenty of potential. A straightforward opportunity to get on the road without a big investment.",
      "price": 3950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left as a project, commuter, or backup ride? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone handy or anyone who just needs inexpensive wheels without spending a fortune. A straightforward, no-nonsense car with good value for the money and lots of potential for the right buyer. Priced to sell and worth a look if you appreciate a budget-friendly deal.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Turn-key project with solid bones and a strong-running powertrain. Starts up, idles, and pulls through the rev range with the kind of mechanical honesty enthusiasts look for in a driver-grade platform. Transmission engages as it should, steering feels connected, and the chassis shows the kind of usable character that makes this a great budget entry for someone who wants a capable commuter, weekend wrenching project, or parts-friendly platform. It\u2019s not a show car and has cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but the fundamentals are there and it presents as a worthwhile, affordable way into ownership.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Cheap driver. Runs, moves, gets the job done. Rough around the edges, priced to sell fast. No fluff.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of well-worn character that turns heads for all the right reasons\u2014a scrappy, honest machine with presence, personality, and plenty of story left to write. It\u2019s the sort of ride that makes a perfect budget commuter, weekend tinker project, or backup car for someone who values potential over polish. If you\u2019ve been looking for an affordable set of wheels with charm and opportunity, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
